    <item>
      <title>中国水泥制造商 99% 的神秘股价暴跌与追加保证金通知有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/margin-call-cited-for-mystery-stock-crash-in-china-cement-maker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国天瑞集团水泥有限公司表示，上周该公司股价突然下跌，引发了一名大股东的追加保证金通知，这解释了股价大幅下跌、导致其市值几乎全部蒸发的背后原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/margin-call-cited-for-mystery-stock-crash-in-china-cement-maker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 03:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
